1476.6]}, {"text": "16", "bbox": [642.6, 1458.4, 659.3, 1476.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [700.1, 1458.4, 708.4, 1476.6]}, {"text": "7", "bbox": [747.1, 1458.4, 755.4, 1476.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [796.3, 1458.4, 804.5, 1476.6]}, {"text": "7", "bbox": [843.3, 1458.4, 851.5, 1476.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [892.4, 1458.4, 900.7, 1476.6]}, {"text": "12", "bbox": [931.0, 1458.4, 947.7, 1476.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [988.4, 1458.4, 996.7, 1476.6]}, {"text": "14", "bbox": [1027.0, 1458.4, 1043.8, 1476.6]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [1084.5, 1458.4, 1092.8, 1476.6]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [919.9, 1438.4, 953.3, 1456.6]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [823.7, 1438.4, 857.3, 1456.6]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [727.6, 1438.4, 761.2, 1456.6]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [631.5, 1438.4, 665.0, 1456.6]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [1015.9, 1438.4, 1049.4, 1456.6]}, {"text": "2014 - 2018", "bbox": [1091.6, 1438.4, 1172.5, 1456.6]}, {"text": "Years ended December 31,", "bbox": [799.5, 1418.4, 984.3, 1436.6]}, {"text": "93", "bbox": [1129.6, 1458.4, 1146.3, 1476.6]}, {"text": "A reconciliation follows of the funded status for our qualified and SERP plans at the end of the measurement", "bbox": [187.5, 58.0, 1145.0, 81.7]}, {"text": "period to the amounts recognized in the balance sheet at December 31, 2008:", "bbox": [187.5, 81.6, 885.0, 105.3]}, {"text": "The weighted-average assumptions used to determine benefit obligations for our qualified and SERP plans at", "bbox": [187.5, 394.5, 1148.6, 418.2]}, {"text": "December 31 follows:", "bbox": [187.5, 418.1, 384.7, 441.8]}, {"text": "We evaluate our pension plan assumptions annually and update them as necessary. The discount rate", "bbox": [187.5, 558.0, 1091.2, 581.7]}, {"text": "assumptions for our benefit obligation track with high grade corporate bond yield and yearly adjustments", "bbox": [187.5, 581.6, 1110.8, 605.3]}, {"text": "reflect any changes to those bond yields. Compensation increase assumptions reflect historical calendar year", "bbox": [187.5, 605.3, 1151.9, 628.9]}, {"text": "compensation increases.", "bbox": [187.5, 628.9, 417.9, 652.5]}, {"text": "Here are the components of our net periodic benefit cost for our qualified and SERP pension plans at", "bbox": [187.5, 658.8, 1077.9, 682.4]}, {"text": "December 31:", "bbox": [187.5, 682.4, 318.4, 706.0]}, {"text": "Our pension plan asset allocations by category are:", "bbox": [187.5, 926.1, 640.1, 949.8]}, {"text": "The pension plan assets are managed to maximize total return over the long term while providing sufficient", "bbox": [187.5, 1135.1, 1130.1, 1158.8]}, {"text": "liquidity and current return to satisfy the cash flow requirements of the plan. Reflecting the long-term time", "bbox": [187.5, 1158.7, 1119.8, 1182.4]}, {"text": "horizon of pension obligations, we currently allocate 80 percent to 85 percent of the pension portfolio to", "bbox": [187.5, 1182.4, 1105.0, 1206.0]}, {"text": "equity investments, which are priced from highly observable and actively traded markets. The remainder of", "bbox": [187.5, 1206.0, 1128.5, 1229.6]}, {"text": "the portfolio is allocated to fixed-maturity investments and cash.", "bbox": [187.5, 1229.6, 755.5, 1253.3]}, {"text": "Our pension plan assets included 642,113 shares of the company’s common stock, which had a fair value of", "bbox": [187.5, 1259.5, 1148.4, 1283.1]}, {"text": "$19 million and $25 million at December 31, 2008 and 2007, respectively. The defined benefit pension plan", "bbox": [187.5, 1283.1, 1151.3, 1306.8]}, {"text": "did not purchase or sell any shares of our common stock during 2008 and 2007. The company paid", "bbox": [187.5, 1306.7, 1068.8, 1330.4]}, {"text": "$1 million in cash dividends on our common stock to the pension plan in both 2008 and 2007.", "bbox": [187.5, 1330.4, 1032.2, 1354.0]}, {"text": "In 2009, we expect to contribute approximately $33 million to our qualified plan. We expect to make the", "bbox": [187.5, 1360.2, 1106.0, 1383.9]}, {"text": "following benefit payments for our qualified and SERP plans, which reflect expected future service:", "bbox": [187.5, 1383.9, 1055.6, 1407.5]}, {"text": "The estimated costs to be amortized from accumulated other comprehensive income into net periodic", "bbox": [187.5, 1493.9, 1086.3, 1517.5]}, {"text": "benefit cost over the next year for our plans are a $1 million actuarial gain and a $1 million prior service cost.", "bbox": [187.5, 1517.5, 1156.0, 1541.2]}]}